{"tid":121050,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"韓韓館渣嫁","createTime":"2017-02-15T02:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T05:19:53.000Z","uid":31521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c3f7adb9e18fd213ac9b7df0132d59f58f0241c","tid":121050,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:16:09.000Z","msg":"尋晚情人節 就算明知會俾人劏都照同女女出街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去尖沙咀韓韓館韓燒 因為早幾個月去食見佢服務態度都幾好 起碼好過旺角嗰間 野食又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋問過幾間得佢有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但今次去好似轉哂人 無咁好笑容 無所謂 佢地唔係賣笑<br />\n多人食 野食出得慢 熟食又無 又漏單都算 旺呀嘛<br />\n最大問題係個經理 塊面由頭西到尾 講野又臭串 對下屬西就算啦 對客都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨尾截單 有檯兩公婆聽唔到 照落單 俾條撚屌嘈 話係個客問題自己無問題 又話唔驚人放上fb唱佢 嘈左一輪 嘈到差d開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n顧客至上？服務態度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺角嗰間態度好差 諗住去尖沙咀就好好啦 點知一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備send email投訴叫間舖一係炒左個撚屌經理 一係執7左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲們咪再去呢間西舖食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b9eaf36b13cfc7fbbc91fcdd1566f3765f2995","tid":121050,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"有無其他巴絲食過呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2051fd4d5265706d3e7638d29fb33e40de636bcd","tid":121050,"uid":7729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"旺角食過<br />\n上年第一次食幾好<br />\n今年再食撞正個經理都幾西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09c8d469019faf6d5c130394e53d796c6d213de","tid":121050,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"點解仲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e33966c1f0612e96b042a1eceee9cc6ffe15ad9","tid":121050,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"當面講<br />\n你咁撚格衰<br />\n唔怪得今日得閒開工"}]}